Cartpole task conventions are informed by DeepMind Control Suite cartpole
and Gymnasium CartPole. The MJCF shipped in physlab is authored for this
project.

Franka pick-place task conventions are informed by MuJoCo Menagerie
franka_emika_panda (BSD-3-Clause), robosuite Lift, and Eureka-style Franka
tasks. The MJCF shipped in physlab is authored for this project for the
v0.1 headless state-vector target.
